Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去后面！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改朝换代！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标只有慈光帝一人！
